Package jadex.planlib

The planlib contains ready-to-use plans and capabilities.

See:
          Description

Capabilities
AMS Capability for agent management system (AMS) functionality.
DF The df capability has all necessay plans, beliefs and goals for all activities concerned with df functionality.
DFMobile The df capability has all necessay plans, beliefs and goals for all activities concerned with df functionality.
Ping The ping capability helps integrating ping behaviour for agents.
Protocols The protocols capability enables an easy goal-driven usage of some often used FIPA protocols.
ProtocolsMobile The protocols capability enables an easy goal-driven usage of some often used FIPA protocols.
StartAgents The start agents capability helps starting agents.
Test The Test capability is responsible for tracking test results and publishes results either to a test center or on console.
TestCenter Test center capability The Test center capability is the generic functionality for a test center.
 

Package jadex.planlib Description

The planlib contains ready-to-use plans and capabilities. See the separate planlib documentation for more details.
